# <type>[optional scope][!]: <description>
#
# [optional body]
#
# [optional footer(s)]
#
# Core types (Conventional Commits 1.0.0):
#   feat:     a new feature
#   fix:      a bug fix
#
# Common additional types:
#   docs, style, refactor, perf, test, build, ci, chore, revert
#
# Breaking changes:
#   Use ! before ':' and/or add a footer:
#   BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
#
# Example: feat(shell): add fzf history preview
# Example: fix(env)!: remove deprecated variable support
# Example:
#   refactor(git): simplify aliases
#
#   Refs: #123
